# Performs the simulations in the articles.

# files:

1. 1_simulations.R

Performs all simulations and saves output fit files to disk. Takes a bit to run as it fits all models.
run it with source.
results are saved to ./data/simulation/

2. 2_tables_plots.R

Uses the saved fit files to produce the table and two plots in the article. The table is printed and
plots are both printed and saved to ./data/simulation/
run it with source.

3. helper.R. contains helper functions. no need to source it. The other two files do it.

-- ignore other files in this folder.
